					<tr valign="top">
						<td width="10" class="o">*</td>
						<td class="o">Malt is made from dried barley sprouts. That is, unhulled barley is watered to give out sprouts. It has digestive enzymes that degrade starch to simple sugars and helps digestion.</td>
					</tr>
